I"n<ol>
  <li>Download &amp; Install HAXM:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget https://software.intel.com/sites/default/files/managed/19/94/haxm-macosx_v6_1_1.zip
unzip haxm-macosx_v6_1_1.zip
sudo ./haxm-macosx_v6_1_1/silent_install.sh
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Download Android SDK:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget http://dl.google.com/android/android-sdk_r24.4.1-macosx.zip
unzip android-sdk_r24.4.1-macosx.zip
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Install Android Dependencies:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>echo y | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update sdk -a -u -f -t android-25
echo y | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update sdk -a -u -f -t platform-tools
echo y | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update sdk -a -u -f -t build-tools-24.0.0
echo y | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update sdk -a -u -f -t extra-google-google_play_services
echo y | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update sdk -a -u -f -t sys-img-x86-google_apis-25
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Create AVD:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>echo no | ./android-sdk-macosx/tools/android create avd -t "android-25" -b google_apis/x86 -c 1024M -s 480x800 -n test --snapshot
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Enable Hardware Keyboard:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>echo "hw.keyboard=yes" &gt;&gt; ~/.android/avd/test.avd/config.ini
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run Emulator:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>./android-sdk-macosx/tools/emulator64-x86 -avd test -no-audio
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

